arts.sum: AC Milan have officially announced the departure of midfielder Ismaël Bennacer to Olympique Marseille. The Algerian international joins the French club on a loan deal with an option to buy, marking the end of his five-and-a-half-year tenure with the Rossoneri. The post OFFICIAL: Ismael Bennacer Joins Marseille appeared first on FootItalia.com.
